keyMappings:
unmap J
unmap K
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
searchEngines:
!w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
!yt: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s
!rust: https://doc.rust-lang.org/std/?search=%s Rust
!docs: https://docs.rs/%s Docsrs
!map: www.google.com/maps/search/%s
!maps: www.google.com/maps/search/%s
!aur: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/?K=%s ArchWiki
!ar: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php?search=%s Aur
!scry: https://scryfall.com/search?q=q=-is%3Aub+date%3C2025+%s Scryfall
!cpp: https://en.cppreference.com/mwiki/index.php?title=Special%3ASearch&search=%s
!draw: https://www.cardmarket.com/en/Magic/Users/DrawstepGD/Offers/Singles?name=%s drawstep
